      <title>盐帽增加从房屋自由核心小组领导</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/salt-cap-increase-gets-boost-from-house-freedom-caucus-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守派众议院自由核心小组的负责人周一预测，国会将在州和地方税收减免上筹集10,000美元的上限，这一标志表明赤字鹰队不会阻止今年晚些时候盐的变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/salt-cap-increase-gets-boost-from-house-freedom-caucus-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 14:46:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈佛说，这暂时冻结了员工，教职员工的招聘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/harvard-temporarily-freezes-hiring-of-staff-faculty-amid-trump-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学正在暂时停顿雇用教职员工和教职员工，因为特朗普政府削减联邦资金的风险威胁到美国大学的财务状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/harvard-temporarily-freezes-hiring-of-staff-faculty-amid-trump-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 14:29:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么欧盟合作伙伴有足够的维克多·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）的石墙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/why-hungary-s-orban-is-stonewalling-the-eu-and-what-the-bloc-can-do-about-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克多·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）通常是欧盟中奇怪的人，尤其是自从俄罗斯入侵乌克兰以来。基本上，他一直在反对西方的努力来获得基辅的援助，并在呼吁将集团对俄罗斯的制裁予以解除时唯一的声音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/why-hungary-s-orban-is-stonewalling-the-eu-and-what-the-bloc-can-do-about-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 14:13:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院拒绝BMC，IBM免除了16亿美元的奖励</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/ibm-spared-1-6-billion-award-as-supreme-court-rejects-bmc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院拒绝恢复针对国际商业机器公司的16亿美元裁决，该公司被KKR＆amp; Co.的BMC软件违反了客户的许可协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/ibm-spared-1-6-billion-award-as-supreme-court-rejects-bmc</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 13:35:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院拒绝共和党支持的竞标，以制止气候诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/supreme-court-rebuffs-gop-backed-bid-to-stop-climate-suits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院拒绝考虑19个共和党经营的州的异常出价，以使一套试图让石油和天然气公司对气候变化负责的诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/supreme-court-rebuffs-gop-backed-bid-to-stop-climate-suits</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 13:33:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院将审查禁止LGBTQ“转化疗法”的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/supreme-court-will-review-ban-on-lgbtq-conversion-therapy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院同意考虑是否通过禁止有执照的辅导员试图改变儿童的性取向或性别认同来违反宪法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/supreme-court-will-review-ban-on-lgbtq-conversion-therapy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 13:32:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大前往美国的旅行在关税，国民威胁的情况下下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/canadian-travel-to-us-plummets-amid-tariff-statehood-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大人似乎在唐纳德·特朗普总统对自己的国家的主权和经济威胁中，放弃前往美国的公路旅行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/canadian-travel-to-us-plummets-amid-tariff-statehood-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 13:24:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚总理踢出联盟合作伙伴作为收视率潜水</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/estonian-premier-kicks-out-coalition-partner-as-ratings-plummet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚总理克里斯汀·米歇尔（Kristen Michal）在政府的批准评级达到了二十年来最低的情况下，从联盟中撤出了社会民主党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/estonian-premier-kicks-out-coalition-partner-as-ratings-plummet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 11:38:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国绿党在谈话之前拒绝国防支出计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/germany-s-greens-won-t-support-draft-debt-package-in-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的绿党拒绝了一项债务筹集的方案，该方案将在国防和基础设施支出中释放数十亿欧元，这可能会损害在顾问弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）的旗舰政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/germany-s-greens-won-t-support-draft-debt-package-in-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 11:10:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
